edu.cmu.cs.crystal.test
Class AnnotatedTest

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.cs.crystal.test.AnnotatedTest

public class AnnotatedTest
extends java.lang.Object

An analysis test that uses test annotations ( PassingTest, FailingTest, UseAnalyses ) to determine which analyses to run, and whether or not the given file is a test. This test will examine every Java file in your test workspace!

Author:
Nels E. Beckman
